$ Perl: in place editing
@ in place editing

Without backup:
`perl -pi -e 's!REGEXP!REPLACEMENT!' file`

With backup:
`perl -pi.bak -e 's!REGEXP!REPLACEMENT!' file`

{ Recursivly

code {
for f in $(grep -R --include=*.cpp REGEXP); do perl -pi -e 's!REGEXP!REPLACEMENT!' $f; done
code }

}

